For Indo-Aryan languages with Devanagari or closely related scripts, translation consistently improves over zero-shot. IndicTrans2 achieves high quality for these pairs, the structural proximity to Hindi, the dominant Indic language in NMT training data, helps. Routing through English allows both models to summarize in their
